Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:16.53,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,O,0000,0000,0000,,Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:21.82,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oneesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:24.74,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,O,0000,0000,0000,,You're on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:26.90,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,O,0000,0000,0000,,Why not go talk to a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:29.49,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No one wants to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.05,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather just take a nap here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:36.94,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.22,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:49.15,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:51.01,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:53.28,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:54.67,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:57.82,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, would you like to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:00:59.70,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,play a game with me?
