Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone, you perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I already explained that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:56.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:03:00.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I needed to do something to \Noverwrite her death flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:03.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Like I believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:09.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:11.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:15.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Akane, you should be more careful around
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:19.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,a perv who'd kiss a defenseless girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:20.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:22.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,If Souta-kun wants to be a perv,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:26.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,he should have just said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:30.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't break her flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't just \Nbrush people off, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:39.32,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't break her conquest flag, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:44.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:47.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:49.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:00.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive. You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real Sou-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,She tackled him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Are they a couple, or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:09.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she on top of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about you this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get a hold of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom and dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Also Oneesan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Oneesan? You're an only \Nchild, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don't remember, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:30.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I've known Sou-kun since we were kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun transferred \Naway in middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,and I haven't seen him in two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's gotten so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in this class when you \Nshould be with the second-years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:50.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, last year, I was studying overseas,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,so I ended up a year behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,This was my seat! Right next to Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:05:00.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think he'd transfer \Naway while I was out sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:01.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,What a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:02.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:06.03,Kiku_eye_05:03,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Kiku's Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:06.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun, you look like you're warn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:10.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can sleep on my lap \Nand I'll clean your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You liked that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:13.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that'll make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:14.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's being too nice to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:16.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,She's spoiling him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:18.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,She's an older sister type!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! Terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:27.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,This is where you're living?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You just feel terrible \Nfor Sou-kun, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Not you, too, Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:33.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You already knew he was living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:36.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Kikuno-senpai started crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,so I started crying, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Akane-chan, so you're \Ncrying for Sou-kun, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,When did Akane-chan and Nanami-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:46.03,Kiku_eye_05:42,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Kiku's Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,get so close to Sou-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:51.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun is spending time with other girls, \Nand he kept them secret from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okiku-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:00.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,She went crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:01.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan's happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:02.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Akane-chan and Nanami-chan, \Nyou're both good girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I approve!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of Sou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:14.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of him with Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:16.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:22.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually happy the two \Nof them are getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sacrifice me for their friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.95,Kiku_eye_06:27,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Kiku's Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun looks so lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:35.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure both of them \Nstay good friends with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:36.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,On, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I let \NSouta-kun become lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a failure of a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay like this, \Nwe can all be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:46.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some kind of dark art?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,So that's when I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:04.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Souta, does Kikuno have a flag, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sibling love flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:11.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what makes \Nher act like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Try breaking her sister flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:16.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You told me not to break \Nthem this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:19.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to end up \Nbeing treated like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:21.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,a little brother your \Nentire life at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You like being a little \Nbrother that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:30.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That should be enough for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:31.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:32.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:34.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Telling Nanami-chan a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You should let me in on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:40.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.19,leave_alone_07:42,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're just embarrassed \Nbecause other girls are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Silly boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem to have been effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The flag dodged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Dodged it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, at mach speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.46,tea_club_08:00,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Tea club
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:11.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuukishibara Tsumugi, the Elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that she's been here since \Nbefore the school was founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,She's in our class. \NDidn't you notice her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:23.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But why... aren't you wearing a skirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how to wear \NJapanese clothes properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's forgetting tradition \Nbecause of the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, can we do something \Nabout this, granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:36.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,That building was constructed \Nwhen the school was founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:39.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to take some \Nsignificant work to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:42.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese population is dropping, \Nand we don't have a large budget—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:44.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,getting the place rebuilt \Nis a tall order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:46.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Please do something for Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:50.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Young'uns these days rely \Non others far too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You should try to do something on your—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:57.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's enough nonsense \Nfor one day, granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You call this "nonsense," Mimori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come in here with shoes on, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,You called for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,so you already had \Nsomething in mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the student council \Npresident you can depend on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,My name: Seiteikouji Mimori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:16.12,pres_09:13,,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council President
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Student council president?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:22.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be faster to just \Nrebuild the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:24.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I've already called \Nin the professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Professionals?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:31.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Hatagaya Academy's Engineering \NResearch Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:34.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why does the school even have \Nan organization like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:35.97,Takumi_09:35,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,Engineering here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:37.84,engineering_09:37,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,Engineering Research Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:40.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can see you wrecked another place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:41.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:42.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,How long will it take for you to fix this \Nplace up so he can live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:47.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to do something as \Nsoon as possible for Sou-kun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:51.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to take a \Nmonth to do all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,That might be different if we could \Nget some more people on the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Then will this work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:55.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're living in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,If we'd only known sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I asked the class to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing this in a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:18.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to thank you all \Nfor listening to my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I owe you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad, Souta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to all \Nof you, Akane, Okiku-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.65,Kiku_eye_05:42,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H7242DD&}Akane's eye
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a wonderful smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:43.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Just seeing it makes me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:55.63,bliss_10:48,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Bliss
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:52.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a cake made \Nout of bliss itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.63,poet_10:52,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Poet-san
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-chan, you're a poet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:10:59.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Souta, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:10.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's doing it out of their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't return goodwill with goodwill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:17.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You keep it in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:20.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,It will grow inside you, and change you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:24.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,and then one day you'll grow into
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:27.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,a person that can have \Ngoodwill towards others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:28.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:39.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a whole different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Keep flattering me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do a single thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,We only have finishing \Ntouches left to make,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,so feel free to start moving in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Time to finish this bad boy up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:52.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get this by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, could you help me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I need a man to help me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm sorry if I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:21.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're right. I'm a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,People always treat me like a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:28.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time someone thought \NI was a guy the first time we talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:40.00,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These are friendship flags, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:41.82,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,How do I destroy these...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.32,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Can I even destroy these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:47.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,My nice is Touzokuyama Megumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Hatate-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:50.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:52.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Then you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:55.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Megumu, Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:58.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell men are friends when \Nthey call each other by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Men, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in our class calls
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,me Megu like I'm a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:06.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's up with that uniform, Megumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:12.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan said I look \Na lot cuter this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:15.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,and got approval from the school \Nto have me dress this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:17.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister must be a tough cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:20.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who understands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.57,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you smell so good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.70,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,And your skin's so soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:30.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, do you need some help—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:32.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:35.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:41.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I always help couples find new partners!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're not helping at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,We were just being friendly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:49.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:52.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Men and women can be great friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.35,clench_13:49,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,725)}Clench
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane, Megumu is a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Look at his uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:14:00.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:01.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:04.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I never saw Megu-chan \Nwith the girls in PE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone still calls me Megu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I take my eyes off of you for a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,and you're already with another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:17.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I... just don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:21.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-nee! Megumu isn't a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Look he's wearing a men's uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:28.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but Megu-chan's always \Nin the girls' bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:33.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,When I go to the men's bathroom, \Neveryone always gets uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:37.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,So the girls are okay with \Nme using the girls' bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:38.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you've been, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? You couldn't find another guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate is the only one \Nin this dorm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:57.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,According to the rules, any dorm with \Na single resident will be shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:59.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,You tell us this now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:02.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Take away our careless \Nstudent council president!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,You need to have at least five people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Mimori says that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:12.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure you'll get five \Nfriends together in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's a terrible rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:19.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't have any friends, \Nyou do have an "oneechan."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:22.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good! You shouldn't be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll move in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is a men's dorm, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:30.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,It's an old dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry about formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:34.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but there can't just be two of us \Nthere... We're the opposite sex, and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:37.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll move in here, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:40.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:42.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to move in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:43.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Megumu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Three women and one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:47.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,That balances out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Now we only need one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Please not another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know any men...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Nanami-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's just a joke, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:09.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun's good friends with you, Nanami. \NOf course you can come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I wanted to live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't get that corner room,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:17.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not moving in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you can't just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess... it'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:30.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Not the black arts again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I said it'll be fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but why are we all gathering in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:39.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:42.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We all suddenly decided to move in, \Nso you're the only one with any stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Then you didn't have to move in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:46.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No. Everything's going to end if
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,we leave you alone for even a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:52.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's true I'm alone in the world, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:55.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time in a \Nroom of a male friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:00.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It feels more like you've entered your \Nboyfriend's room, not your friend's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,If we're all going to live together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,then we need to decide \Na bunch of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Like who's going to be in charge, \Nor who's on duty for what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:10.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You've sure thought this through, Okiku-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I am the "oneechan," after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,But before that we need to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.85,bath_17:15,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.85,sign1_17:15,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are Bathing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.85,sign2_17:15,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,No Peeking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:19.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I wanted to \Nget in with Sou-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:24.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,like we used to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You mean a really long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,when you were small, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,If you're jealous, you can go \Nahead and call me "oneechan."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:36.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finally fall \Nfor him, Nanami-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:39.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You finally stopped being \Nthat weird "tsundere"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What is that even supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:44.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Akane-chan, are you rooting \Nfor Sou-kun and Nanami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just want
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:50.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,to make Souta-kun happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:53.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Akane-chan, you're a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You're a member of the \N"Make Sou-kun happy" alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What do members of that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:02.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,They watch Sou-kun be \Nhappy and feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:04.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we supposed to be \Nthe ones making him happy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Even Akane can't keep \Nup with her craziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.07,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.71,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get a conversation \Ngoing with Megumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.45,Men_18:18,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Men
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,BG,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A-A "men" flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, we're going \Nto look in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:25.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:29.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to go, \Nwalk straight in, and get an eyeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:29.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Now come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:38.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure that \Nreal men wouldn't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:39.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.23,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.33,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.65,keropon_18:54,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Keropon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:03.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:09.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:12.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That really sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:13.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:19.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.32,Hatate_Souta_19:42,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.14,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.67,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:59.17,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd be able to \Nput up a better fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.47,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,The knight, magician,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:04.29,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,samurai, dragon knight, bishop,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:07.18,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,ninja, thief, summoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.18,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,The magician is troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.63,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, you should \Nget rid of him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:13.94,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,You need the knight for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.44,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,He will always follow the Royal Banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:20.69,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,The bishop acts as a decoy, and \Nthe ninja attacks from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.05,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.70,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what I should have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:26.95,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,Oniisan, you haven't forgotten \Nyour promise, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:30.36,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The person who loses will listen \Nto whatever the winner says.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.34,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.33,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder you're going to tell me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.47,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to tell \Nyou to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:37.64,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:41.84,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't win because I was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.36,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,Above my head I have the "victor" flag,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:47.22,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,and above yours, you \Nhave the "defeat" flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.35,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.35,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.71,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,And in exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:56.48,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,you must learn the ultimate \Ntruth of this world.
